Come on, let's get outta here!

19:15.710 --> 19:17.290
The door's gone!

19:17.290 --> 19:20.290
Where's the door?
Where's the door?

19:20.290 --> 19:26.080
Oh, no, we're stuck --
stuck -- stuck in here forever!

19:26.080 --> 19:29.210
Become a professional ballerina
in three easy lessons

19:29.210 --> 19:31.120
for only $99.99.

19:31.120 --> 19:34.250
both: If only we had the money.

19:34.250 --> 19:37.500
Hey, watchdog,
we could borrow
some money

19:37.500 --> 19:39.210
from that purse
in the closet.

19:39.210 --> 19:42.080
And how would we
pay it back, wiener dog?

19:42.080 --> 19:43.420
Are you low on cash?

19:43.420 --> 19:46.080
Dying to borrow money but don't
know how to pay it back?

19:46.080 --> 19:48.920
Play Super Duper
Legal State Lottery!

19:48.920 --> 19:52.080
The jackpot is up
to $29 trillion!

19:53.120 --> 19:56.920
both, chuckling: Ahhh!

20:03.880 --> 20:05.960
Doggone it!

20:06.960 --> 20:08.880
Horace: We'll win the lottery,
repay the money,

20:08.880 --> 20:11.040
and buy all the cool stuff
we saw on the television.

20:11.040 --> 20:12.290
Quick, everybody --

20:12.290 --> 20:13.330
Panic!

20:13.330 --> 20:16.000
Don't panic.
Creativity has no limits.

20:16.000 --> 20:19.170
I know,
make like fuzzy slippers!

20:23.830 --> 20:25.290
Jasper: Just find
the money, Horace.

20:25.290 --> 20:26.920
She hid it in a shoebox.

20:26.920 --> 20:28.580
Ah, look how cute.

20:28.580 --> 20:31.460
I've just gotta try these on.

20:33.120 --> 20:34.790
The money!

20:34.790 --> 20:36.330
-Yowwww!

20:36.330 --> 20:37.420
Watchdog, help!

20:37.420 --> 20:39.710
The slippers are stealing
the money!

20:39.710 --> 20:42.120
It's just the puppies,
you wiener dog!

20:43.250 --> 20:45.040
Get 'em!

21:00.830 --> 21:02.580
Where did they go?

21:02.580 --> 21:03.960
I feel pretty.

