Welcome to Cruella's
automated closet.

21:09.580 --> 21:12.380
Please keep your paws
inside the coat at all times.

21:12.380 --> 21:15.000
On your left, business suits,
casual suits, law suits.

21:15.000 --> 21:17.750
On your right, evening wear,
swimwear, underwear.

21:17.750 --> 21:18.960
dogs: Yuck!

21:19.920 --> 21:22.210
Bellbottoms and bloomers,
hip-huggers and boots, skirts,

21:22.210 --> 21:24.250
petticoats and pantaloons,
muumuus and miniskirts,

21:24.250 --> 21:26.210
cardigans and kimonos,
tutus and t-shirts,

21:26.210 --> 21:28.670
and, just ahead, lingerie!

21:28.670 --> 21:30.290
Aaaaaaah!

21:30.290 --> 21:32.330
Ohhhh!

21:35.920 --> 21:36.920
Hmm.

21:41.620 --> 21:44.120
Ohh! Why, you!

21:44.120 --> 21:46.830
You know,
with the right belt,

21:46.830 --> 21:48.580
that would look fabulous!

21:50.670 --> 21:53.960
Roger!
Here's the purse right here.

21:55.290 --> 21:56.960
Ah, thank goodness.

21:58.000 --> 21:59.000
We did it.

21:59.000 --> 22:00.710
We returned
Anita's purse

22:00.710 --> 22:03.710
and we saved
the farm!

22:03.710 --> 22:07.170
To think we were
gonna spend that money
like it was ours. Over.

22:07.170 --> 22:08.750
Roger that.

22:08.750 --> 22:12.040
It's just
like posing as
